{"tid":2237914,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"想問問各位係咪無得渣車入長州？","createTime":"2020-10-10T16:07:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T07:30:49.000Z","uid":353358,"like":5,"dislike":110,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"9a63755b425a0c42bdf851e9da9d07278fd7d0d6","tid":2237914,"uid":353358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T16:07:39.000Z","msg":"想問問各位係咪無得渣車入長州？只可以泊係中環碼頭然後搭船過去啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好意思因為未入過長州所以真係唔係好清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（希望各位唔好介意 我係美國返黎 由中學開始係個邊讀書 得xmas同暑假先會返hk 所以唔多唔少對香港印象都模糊左 我自己都覺得應該自我檢討下 因為身為香港人 呢d野係要知道 最後 如果我呢個問題令你地覺得無奈/咋舌 希望多多包涵啦）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7bd967463ee81f33e82fea963de2259036ff0ad","tid":2237914,"uid":6446,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T16:12:05.000Z","msg":"google map"},{"pid":"05d616edcd6296ae70ec12245ad67284f837c23c","tid":2237914,"uid":345342,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T16:12:53.000Z","msg":"少少嘢都要問點做汽車台霸主<br />\nQuit撚咗佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d18325197897a4afdc59f92660e1a124f545dba","tid":2237914,"uid":136416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T16:13:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>［20號就截！］德國聯署逐步圖文教學 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2237513\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2237513</a><br />\n有12人受緊苦</blockquote>"},{"pid":"292bcd66a8e1eb970b6776f9c404c34